Hello, this a tutorial about making the PvP-levels.

[b]Difficulty: 1/10[/b]
[b]Requirements: Copy + Paste + Delta source.[/b]
[b][size=18pt]Everything is done in Client.java[/size][/b]

Open up Client.java and search for:
[code]				sendQuest("Level: " + wildyLevel, 199);[/code]

You should see something like this:
[code]if (isInWilderness(absX, absY, 1))
		{
			if (!hasWildySign)
			{
				hasWildySign = true;
				outStream.createFrame(208);
				outStream.writeWordBigEndian_dup(197);
				sendQuest("Level: " + wildyLevel, 199);


			}
			int level = ((absY - 3520) / 8) + 1;
			if (level != wildyLevel)
			{
				wildyLevel = level;
				sendQuest("Level: " + wildyLevel, 199);

			}
		}[/code]



